From 8a3c7f2b9e1d4f6a0c2b8e5d7a3f1c4e6b8d0a2f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Shin <shining@uniontech.com>
Date: Wed, 21 May 2026 10:37:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] fix(randr): use mode-space coordinates for CRTC bounds checking

f_transform already includes Translate(crtc.x, crtc.y), so the display_box
passed to pixman_f_transform_bounds must be in mode space {0, 0, w, h},
not framebuffer space {crtc.x, crtc.y, ...}. Using framebuffer-space
coordinates causes double counting of position and scale, leading to
BadMatch on dual-screen or scale>1.0 scenarios.

f_transform已包含Translate(crtc.x, crtc.y)，传入pixman_f_transform_bounds
的display_box必须是mode空间坐标{0,0,w,h}，而非framebuffer空间。
使用framebuffer空间坐标会导致位置和缩放被双重计算，在双屏或缩放>1.0
场景下引发BadMatch错误。

Log: 修复CRTC边界检查中display_box坐标空间错误
PMS: BUG-276065
Influence: 修复双屏缩放>1.0或CRTC位置非原点时SetScreenSize错误返回BadMatch的问题，
确保所有场景下屏幕尺寸校验正确。
---
 randr/rrscreen.c | 6 +++---
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

Index: xorg-server/randr/rrscreen.c
===================================================================
--- xorg-server.orig/randr/rrscreen.c
+++ xorg-server/randr/rrscreen.c
@@ -269,9 +269,9 @@ ProcRRSetScreenSize(ClientPtr client)
 
         if (!RRCrtcIsLeased(crtc) && mode) {
             struct pixman_box16 display_box = {
-                crtc->x, crtc->y,
-                crtc->x + mode->mode.width,
-                crtc->y + mode->mode.height
+                0, 0,
+                mode->mode.width,
+                mode->mode.height
             };
             pixman_f_transform_bounds(&crtc->f_transform, &display_box);
 
